# Instagram Graph API Credentials
# IMPORTANT: You need an Instagram Business or Creator account
# Connected to a Facebook Page

# Step-by-step setup:
# 1. Convert your Instagram to Business/Creator account (in Instagram app settings)
# 2. Connect Instagram to a Facebook Page (in Instagram app → Account → Linked Accounts)
# 3. Create a Facebook App at https://developers.facebook.com/apps/
# 4. Add "Instagram Graph API" product
# 5. Get Instagram User ID: https://graph.facebook.com/v18.0/me/accounts (shows connected IG accounts)
# 6. Generate Long-lived Access Token (valid 60 days)

INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID=your_ig_business_account_id_here
FACEBOOK_PAGE_ID=your_connected_fb_page_id_here
FACEBOOK_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_long_lived_access_token_here
